<ITEM><HI>Inf. II</HI> The Joyes of Heaven are wonderful. <HI>p. 95</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Inf. III.</HI> The Souls of Men who Dy in their Sins, are after <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> Death of their Bodies <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">n a Miserable estate. <HI>p. 99</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>USE. Exhort.</HI> Let us make sure of this one thing, that <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">hen our Bodies dye, our Souls may go to be with the Spirits <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> Just Men. <HI>p. 10<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"></HI></ITEM>
