<ITEM><HI>Prop. IV.</HI> None besides the Children of God shall have a blessed Resurrection. <HI>p. 155</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>USE Inf. I.</HI> All the Ch<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ldren of God are infinitely beholden to the Lord Jesus Christ. <HI>p. 163</HI></ITEM>
